        "class": "bld",
        "text": "14",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "shalt thou not know",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " it] It is the peaceful and unprotected condition of the people, along with their wealth, that tempts Gog to invade them. LXX., however, reads: shalt thou not ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "stir thyself up",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
